Script usage:
-edit mysql_simplebackup.php and set valid values for property $default_config (hostname, username and password to connect to MySQL)
-run the script
-enter name of the database you want to backup
-click "Create backup" - it will create database with name {DB_NAME}_backup
-do whatever you want with backuped database
-in case of previous step's fail click "Restore backup" button (warning! {DB_NAME}_backup database will be dropped